So for the people in the business, sales and marketing, the idea was to know how much

00:05:47.279 --> 00:05:52.760
am I going to sell to my partner, to my distributor, this year, but also next year.

00:05:52.760 --> 00:05:57.799
So they want to have visibility on the sales for the next 18 to 24 months, and all this

