So, we are going to upload for the volumes.

00:39:22.840 --> 00:39:24.840
And some parameters.

00:39:24.840 --> 00:39:25.840
Stock mean.

00:39:25.840 --> 00:39:28.840
We can see it's different depending on the product and the country.

00:39:29.840 --> 00:39:32.840
Country especially because here it's only the product number 14.

