Maybe five months.

00:39:38.840 --> 00:39:39.840
So, we can customize everything.

00:39:39.840 --> 00:39:41.840
Stock mean.

00:39:41.840 --> 00:39:42.840
Frequency of supply.

00:39:42.840 --> 00:39:45.840
Reorder quantity that I put here at one by default.

00:39:45.840 --> 00:39:47.840
And the delivery time.

00:39:53.840 --> 00:39:57.840
And after, we can calculate replenishment plan.

00:39:57.840 --> 00:39:58.840
So, we can download this.

00:39:58.840 --> 00:40:02.840
It can be our conclusion of the review for distributor.

00:40:02.840 --> 00:40:04.840
To see, okay, validate this replenishment plan.

00:40:04.840 --> 00:40:06.840
Or we can ask us to advance some supplies.

00:40:06.840 --> 00:40:08.840
Or maybe to postpone some supplies.

00:40:08.840 --> 00:40:14.840
If the sales team want to keep some sales for the next quarter or the next year.

00:40:14.840 --> 00:40:17.840
And we can look at this at different perspective.

00:40:17.840 --> 00:40:20.840
From a distributor point of view.

00:40:20.840 --> 00:40:22.840
When the product need to arrive.

00:40:22.840 --> 00:40:24.840
Supplier date.

00:40:24.840 --> 00:40:25.840
When they need to be shipped.

00:40:26.840 --> 00:40:29.840
And also everything.

00:40:29.840 --> 00:40:31.840
Distributors and suppliers date all together.

00:40:31.840 --> 00:40:34.840
So, here we are in Bangladesh, for example.

00:40:34.840 --> 00:40:35.840
Product 14.

00:40:35.840 --> 00:40:38.840
The first few months are frozen.

00:40:38.840 --> 00:40:40.840
And after free horizon.

00:40:40.840 --> 00:40:45.840
And the DRP is calculated at either free or free horizon.

00:40:45.840 --> 00:40:49.840
You can see here, 88 units need to arrive in August.

00:40:49.840 --> 00:40:54.840
So, they need to be shipped in July.

00:40:55.840 --> 00:40:56.840
Okay.

00:40:56.840 --> 00:41:01.840
So, here is a bigger example of this swap.

00:41:01.840 --> 00:41:05.840
To show you how it can be scalable to more countries.

00:41:05.840 --> 00:41:06.840
Same program.

00:41:06.840 --> 00:41:09.840
Just more lines to proceed.

00:41:09.840 --> 00:41:13.840
And to calculate this, it takes maybe 5 seconds.

00:41:13.840 --> 00:41:15.840
In R, it's very fast.

00:41:15.840 --> 00:41:18.840
And if there are many products, maybe 200 products.

00:41:18.840 --> 00:41:21.840
If you make it 1,000, it's just 7 seconds.

00:41:21.840 --> 00:41:22.840
It's very fast.

