00:48:40.840 --> 00:48:42.840
First expired, first out.

00:48:43.840 --> 00:48:45.840
Before, for example, we look at our stocks.

00:48:45.840 --> 00:48:47.840
Let's say that we have 1,000 units in stock.

00:48:47.840 --> 00:48:53.840
